curam.common.util.xml.dom

Class Namespace

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Content
      • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Namespace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomWrapper

    public class Namespace
extends Content
    A Namespace provides a method to avoid element name conflicts. This implementation wraps a dom4j Namespace.
